Aquaserv SA, a Romanian utility,
awarded a 17.5 million-lei ($5 million) contract to upgrade a
water-treatment plant in the central county of Mures to  Edas-
Exim SRL .  The contract to improve the water-treatment facility in
Tarnaveni was initially estimated at 18.4 million lei and
attracted three bids, according to  a notice  published today on
